      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, slice the <strong>baby button mushrooms</strong> roughly</p><p>Dissolve the <strong>beef stock mix</strong> and <strong>tomato paste</strong> with 300ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[500ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>beef</strong> <strong>stock</strong></p><p>When your mince has browned, add the<strong> sliced mushrooms </strong>and <strong>butternut squash cubes </strong>to the pan and cook for 1-2 min</p>",
