      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>beef</strong> <strong>stock</strong>, <strong>Dijon mustard</strong> and <strong>Henderson's Relish</strong> with a generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and cook, covered, for 20-25 min or until the sauce has reduced, the squash has softened and the the mince is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>lighter beef & squash stew</strong></p>",
