    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the potatoes and parsnips to a low heat with a small knob of <strong>butter</strong> and a splash of <strong>milk</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and mash until smooth</p><p>Chop the <strong>parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks</p>",
